prodNameC: 羅氏可霸斯免疫分析球蛋白E第二代檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
M        Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL:
         Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.
R1      Anti-IgE-Ab~biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL:
         Biotinylated monoclonal anti-IgE antibody (mouse) 2.5 mg/L;
         phosphate buffer 85 mmol/L, pH 6.5; preservative.
R2      Anti-IgE-Ab~Ru(bpy)2+3 (black cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL:
         Monoclonal anti-IgE antibody (mouse) labeled with ruthenium
         complex 5.5 mg/L; phosphate buffer 85 mmol/L, pH 6.5; preservative.

CalSet - working solutions
• IGE Cal1: 2 bottles, each containing 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
• IGE Cal2: 2 bottles, each containing 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
IgE (human) in two concentration ranges (approx. 1 IU/mL or 2.4 ng/mL and approx. 100 IU/mL or 240 ng/mL) in an equine serum matrix; preservative.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: 用於體外定量檢測人類血清及血漿中免疫球蛋白E(IgE)的免疫分析法。總IgE的測定對於過敏性疾病的輔助診斷是有用的。Electro-chemiluminescence immunoassay “ECLIA”是預定使用於 Elecsys和cobas e免疫分析儀上。
